folder: Ave. T & Van Sicklen St., Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Ave. T - Van Sicklen St.
text:
Ave. T. at the N.E. corner of Van Sicklen Street. In the extreme right background, is Lake Street; at the right foreground is Ave. T. The view shows the church and rectory of St. Simon and St. Jude. (R.C.).

April 25, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
